# Design-system bundle (.claude/skills/zenith-design) is design-sync managed.
# Track only what Storybook renders and what the component port reads as input;
# the rest (templates, ui_kits, generated bundles, design-pane preview cards)
# is regenerated by a sync and would just churn.
.claude/*
!.claude/skills/
.claude/skills/*
!.claude/skills/zenith-design/
.claude/skills/zenith-design/*
!.claude/skills/zenith-design/SKILL.md
!.claude/skills/zenith-design/styles.css
!.claude/skills/zenith-design/tokens/
!.claude/skills/zenith-design/stories/
